{"tid":709753,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"集合肉餅食譜(識整好食肉餅的巴絲入)","createTime":"2018-06-20T09:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T08:18:10.000Z","uid":100551,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9e365a897d67b28e072ea148bb57713be2a21b32","tid":709753,"uid":100551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:09:55.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲識整好食的肉餅<br />\n最重要係軟熟<br />\n求教<br />\n<br />\n我老媽整啲肉餅真係太難食...<br />\n難食到可以上美女廚房...硬到掟去對面海都唔爛...<br />\n上網睇有啲食譜又覺得好吹水(教人大大力咁撻嚿肉餅...唔識都知唔得...越撻只會越有「咬口」)<br />\n<br />\n求食神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d8b1926f3b641de316705f11f7d15daa115c11","tid":709753,"uid":57844,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:39:55.000Z","msg":"整肉丸先需要撻, 就咁肉餅煎或蒸都唔駛撻<br />\n其實好易整, 碎豬肉加糖鹽豉油撈到起膠, 鋪滿碟中間加咸蛋<br />\n蒸熟食得. <br />\n想健康D可用多D瘦肉加D麥皮加D水<br />\n唔好用全瘦, 鞋到仆街"},{"pid":"d63a496ca7acced753040884c16dd88a6f2649d3","tid":709753,"uid":48577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:54:01.000Z","msg":"加墨魚膠 冇就加蛋白"},{"pid":"91fa73e99f309b8e23005d157a3121904ab9f3b9","tid":709753,"uid":47888,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T10:04:11.000Z","msg":"唔想煩就落肥肉，一定好食"},{"pid":"07a25608a19c1577987965dfb3da70f6e9853b81","tid":709753,"uid":100551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61d8b1926f3b641de316705f11f7d15daa115c11","tid":709753,"uid":57844,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:39:55.000Z","msg":"整肉丸先需要撻, 就咁肉餅煎或蒸都唔駛撻<br />\n其實好易整, 碎豬肉加糖鹽豉油撈到起膠, 鋪滿碟中間加咸蛋<br />\n蒸熟食得. <br />\n想健康D可用多D瘦肉加D麥皮加D水<br />\n唔好用全瘦, 鞋到仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T10:08:01.000Z","msg":"我諗8成瘦咁上下...<br />\n極限係幾多?"},{"pid":"81b020888ce855e76f9b1c7a7c70102f93399082","tid":709753,"uid":56453,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018